                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When an alchemical golem takes physical damage from a critical hit or is affected by a shatter spell, one glass chamber within its body shatters, spewing alchemical liquid in a @Template[type:emanation|distance:5].</p>\n<p>Roll on the alchemical chambers list to determine which one shatters-on a roll of 1-5, creatures in the area take [[/r 10d6]] damage of the appropriate type. On a roll of 6, creatures must instead save against the sickness effect.</p>"
